      <title>比特币有望创三年来最长的周涨幅纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/bitcoin-btc-on-track-for-longest-weekly-winning-streak-in-over-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币有望连续第七周上涨，因为人们对支持加密货币的特朗普政府的乐观情绪日益高涨，推动了比特币价格创下三年多来最长的连续上涨势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/bitcoin-btc-on-track-for-longest-weekly-winning-streak-in-over-three-years</guid>
